import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { LoguearService } from '../../service/loguear.service'; import { ExamenService } from 'src/app/admin/services/examen.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-home', templateUrl: './home.component.html', styleUrls: ['./home.component.css'] }) export class HomeComponent implements OnInit { loggg : boolean = false listExamn : any; constructor(private loginName:LoguearService,private obtenerNombre:ExamenService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.loginName.getOrganizacionId().subscribe( (data) => {this.loggg= data} ) this.obtenerNombre.getExam().subscribe( (data)=> {this.listExamn=data} ) } }
